ablend.com/new/Jimmy-Buffett-Appeared-Jurassic-World-Odds-You-Saw-Him-72017.html |archive-date=2015-06-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影的技術顧問{{link-en|傑克·霍納（古生物學家）|Jack Horner (paleontologist)|傑克·霍納}}在電影裏客串出演一名遊客<ref name=SR>{{cite web|date= 2015-06-13|url= http://screenrant.com/jurassic-world-easter-eggs-trivia-references/|access-date= 06-08-2015|title= 'Jurassic World' Easter Eggs, Trivia & 'Jurassic Park' References|website= Screenrant|first= Andrew|last= Dyce|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150814104238/http://screenrant.com/jurassic-world-easter-eggs-trivia-references/|archive-date= 2015-08-14|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

==主題分析==
身兼導演及編劇的[[柯林·特雷沃羅|柯林·特雷沃羅]]表示，劇中的基因合成恐龍帝王暴龍反映了人性的黑暗面。這頭恐龍的誕生象徵了商人及顧客的野心，因為人們「渴望更多，但永遠感到不夠，就好像劇中的人希望看到更巨大、更敏捷、更兇猛的恐龍，而商家亦順從市場需求使之問世」。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Maharana|first1=Kabita|title=Jurassic World: Synthetic Indominus Rex embodies the worst human tendencies teases director Colin Trevorrow|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/jurassic-world-synthetic-indominus-rex-embodies-worst-human-tendencies-teases-director-colin-1502955|website=[[國際財經時報|''International Business Times'']]|publisher=IBT Media|date=2015-05-26|accessdate=10-06-2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610133814/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/jurassic-world-synthetic-indominus-rex-embodies-worst-human-tendencies-teases-director-colin-1502955|archive-date=2015-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>他還指出：「此劇亦充分反映了我們對商業利益的渴望。對我而言，帝王暴龍的誕生正體現了這種極需獲得滿足的渴望。」<ref>{{cite web|title=How the dinosaurs in Jurassic World came to life|url=http://www.news.com.au/technology/innovation/how-the-dinosaurs-in-jurassic-world-came-to-life/story-fnjwucti-1227391097262|website=News.com.au|publisher=News Corp Australia|date=10-06-2015|accessdate=10-06-2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610133408/http://www.news.com.au/technology/innovation/how-the-dinosaurs-in-jurassic-world-came-to-life/story-fnjwucti-1227391097262|archive-date=2015-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>電影評論者也注意到這種供應與需要的關係同樣存在於《侏羅紀世界》本身，以及娛樂事業市場之間。<ref>{{cite web|last1=McGovern|first1=Joe|title=Meet Jurassic World's Indominus Rex: 'An abomination and a killer—and on party plates'|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/05/25/meet-new|website=[[娛樂周刊|''Entertainment Weekly'']]|publisher=[[時代華納|Time Inc.]]|date=2015-05-25|accessdate=10-06-2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622002057/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/05/25/meet-new|archive-date=2015-06-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《侏羅紀世界》演員之一的詹士·杜蒙特表示，這部電影的另一主題意識，是「人與環境為一體」及「不制止不良行為的人等同於助長甚至鼓勵這樣的行為」。<ref>{{cite web|title=Jurassic World actor James DuMont talks Nichiren Buddhism and "a deeper shade of blue."|url=http://thankingthespoon.com/2015/06/12/jurassic-world-actor-james-dumont-talks-nichiren-buddhism-and-a-deeper-shade-of-blue/|publisher=Thanking the spoon|date=2015|accessdate=2015-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716120709/http://thankingthespoon.com/2015/06/12/jurassic-world-actor-james-dumont-talks-nichiren-buddhism-and-a-deeper-shade-of-blue/|archive-date=2015-07-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

