2001年3月，《[[侏羅紀公園3|侏羅紀公園3]]》的導演[[喬·約翰斯頓|喬·約翰斯頓]]稱對於第四部作品尚未有任何構思。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.dansjp3page.com/oldnews22.asp |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20010413024442/http://www.dansjp3page.com/oldnews22.asp |archivedate= 2001-04-13 |title= Joe Johnson Speaks |publisher= DansJP3Page.com |date= 08-03-2001 |first= Dan |last= Finkelstein |accessdate= 01-11-2014 |deadurl= yes }}</ref>錄製後期，執行製作人[[史提芬·史匹堡|史提芬·史匹堡]]（[[侏羅紀公園|第一]]及[[侏羅紀公園：迷失世界|第二部]]電影的導演）有了原想放在第三部作品裡的新想法，這為第四部電影的製作打開了大門。<ref name=ZReview>{{cite web|url= http://www.thezreview.co.uk/comingsoon/j/jurassicpark4.htm|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20021102211033/http://www.thezreview.co.uk/comingsoon/j/jurassicpark4.htm|title= Jurassic Park IV Update:|publisher= TheZReview.co.uk|date= 12-06-2002|archivedate= 2002-11-02|access-date= 2015-08-17|dead-url= no}}</ref>同年6月，約翰斯頓表示，史匹堡已有了新的主意，足以將整個系列推至另一個高峰，惟他不會再擔任導演。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/06/13/jurassic-park-iv-probably-but-without-joe-johnston|title= Jurassic Park IV? Probably, But Without Joe Johnston|publisher= IGN.com|date= 2001-06-13|accessdate= 01-11-2014|first= Steve|last= Head|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141102010945/http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/06/13/jurassic-park-iv-probably-but-without-joe-johnston|archive-date= 2014-11-02|dead-url= no}}</ref>他還指出，新的構思跳出了原有的故事框架，暗示了新作品將不再以某一小島作事發地點。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://dansjp3page.com/oldnews32.asp| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20010620182549/http://www.dansjp3page.com/index2.asp| archivedate=2001-06-20| first=Dan| last=Finkelstein| title=JP Series Will Go On Until 'We've Had Enough'| publisher=DansJP3Page.com| date=2001-06-15| accessdate=01-11-2014| deadurl=yes}}</ref>一個月後，飾演第一及第三部電影裡的艾倫·格蘭特博士[[森·尼爾|森·尼爾]]表示，他無法想出能說服他自己繼續演出新電影的理由。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://dansjp3page.com/neill-interview.asp |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20010716223215/http://www.dansjp3page.com/neill-interview.asp |title= Dan Interviews Sam Neill |publisher= www.DansJP3Page.com |date= 09-07-2001 |archivedate= 2001-07-16 |accessdate= 01-11-2014 |first= Dan |last= Finkelstein |deadurl= yes }}</ref>同月，約翰斯頓否認但後來又暗示出現於《侏羅紀公園3》片尾中的[[無齒翼龍|無齒翼龍]]會出現在新作品中。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.ew.com/ew/report/0,6115,167997~1~0~learnaboutjurassicpark,00.html |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20010721080634/http://www.ew.com/ew/report/0,6115,167997~1~0~learnaboutjurassicpark,00.html |title= Dino Might |work= Entertainment Weekly |date= 2001-07-18 |archivedate= 2001-07-21 |first= Liane |last= Bonin |access-date= 2015-08-17 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.suntimes.com/output/pearlman/cst-ftr-cindy23.html |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20010725112851/http://www.suntimes.com/output/pearlman/cst-ftr-cindy23.html |title= 'Jurassic 3' delivers crushing blow |work= Chicago Sun-Times |date= 2001-07-23 |archivedate= 2001-07-25 |first= Cindy |last= Pearlman |access-date= 2015-08-17 |dead-url= no }}</ref>

2002年4月，有報導指第四部電影不會承接前三部的劇情，而其亦將會為整個系列畫上句號。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.comingsoon.net/cgibin/archive/fullnews.cgi?newsid1019220329,75782, |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20020608210635/http://www.comingsoon.net/cgi-bin/archive/fullnews.cgi?newsid1019220329,75782, |title= Jurassic Park 4 in the works? |publisher= ComingSoon.net citing E! Online |date= 2002-04-19 |archivedate= 2002-06-08 |access-date= 2015-08-17 |dead-url= no }}</ref>同年6月，史匹堡在《{{link-en|星志雜誌|Starlog}}》的訪問中表示將會製作第四部電影，故事情節是整個系列中最好的，他亦希望約翰斯頓能繼續擔任導演。<ref name= ZReview />11月4日，尼爾表示可能出演新電影。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.aintitcool.com/node/13725 |title= Sam Neill on 'Jurassic Park 4'!!! |publisher= AintItCool.com |date= 06-11-2002 |accessdate= 01-11-2014 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141102001558/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/13725 |archive-date= 2014-11-02 |dead-url= no }}</ref>三天後，官方宣佈{{link-en|威廉·莫納漢|William Monahan}}為編劇，[[凱斯琳·甘迺迪_(電影監製)|凱斯琳·甘迺迪]]為監製，而史匹堡則繼續擔任執行製片人。<ref>{{cite news | first=Brian | last=Linder | url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/376/376630p1.html | title=''Jurassic Park IV'' Goes Ahead | publisher=IGN | date=07-11-2002 | accessdate=2007-02-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061208120205/http://movies.ign.com/articles/376/376630p1.html | archive-date=2006-12-08 | dead-url=no }}</ref>一個月後，發行商稱電影將會於2005年的暑假上映。<ref>{{cite news |last1=McNary |first1=Dave |last2=Diorio |first2=Carl |title=Early-bird specials |date=2002-12-22 |work=Variety |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117877754.html?categoryid=1019&cs=1 |accessdate=2007-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011212528/http://variety.com/article/VR1117877754.html?categoryid=1019&cs=1 |archive-date=2007-10-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2003年1月，出現於第一及第二部電影的演員[[謝夫·高拔林|謝夫·高拔林]]指，他獲邀繼續於新作品中飾演伊恩·馬爾科姆一角色。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.countingdown.com/movies/jp4/movieinfo/cast?item_id=2763818 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20030207223239/http://www.countingdown.com/movies/jp4/movieinfo/cast?item_id=2763818 |title= More of Goldblum's Cinemania JP4 Talk |publisher= CountingDown.com |date= 07-01-2003 |archivedate= 2003-02-07 |access-date= 2015-08-17 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>同月30日傳出了有關新電影劇情的資訊：恐龍群遷移至[[哥斯達黎加|哥斯達黎加]]，艾倫與伊恩因而追索到國際基因公司的其中一個離岸小島，並發現島上的恐龍繁殖工作經已失控。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/01/30/more-on-jpiv |title= More on JPIV |publisher= IGN.com |date= 2003-01-30 |accessdate= 01-11-2014 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141102010057/http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/01/30/more-on-jpiv |archive-date= 2014-11-02 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.movieweb.com/jurrasic-park-4-plot-details|title= Jurassic Park 4 plot details?|publisher= MovieWeb.com|date= 2003-01-31|accessdate= 01-11-2014|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141125064352/http://www.movieweb.com/jurrasic-park-4-plot-details|archive-date= 2014-11-25|dead-url= no}}</ref>同年4月，[[斯坦·溫斯頓|斯坦·溫斯頓]]的特效製片廠已經為新電影的製作做好了準備。溫斯頓指，這次史匹堡加入了以前不曾用過的橋段，它們均出自[[米高·克賴頓|米高·克賴頓]]筆下的《侏羅紀公園》小說。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.comingsoon.net/cgibin/archive/fullnews.cgi?newsid1050297871,28882, |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20030422211501/http://www.comingsoon.net/cgi-bin/archive/fullnews.cgi?newsid1050297871,28882, |title= Stan Winston Talks Jurassic Park IV! |publisher= .ComingSoon.net |date= 2003-04-14 |archivedate= 2003-04-22 |access-date= 2015-08-17 |dead-url= no }}</ref>同年7月，官方給予了英國演員[[姬拉·麗莉|姬拉·麗莉]]兩個角色選擇。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.countingdown.com/movies/269508/news?item_id=3136091 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20040703031916/http://www.countingdown.com/movies/269508/news?item_id=3136091 |title= Knightley Confirms JP4 Talks? |publisher= CountingDown.com |date= 2003-07-14 |archivedate= 2004-07-03 |quote= There were actually two roles in 'Jurassic Park IV' Steven thought I might fit. First there was the granddaughter part, which wasn't all that big a role; she was only in it at the beginning. The other part he was considering for me was substantially larger, but I won't go into any details in case I make Steven angry (laughs). ... I truly don't know if I'll end up getting either part or not. The script is pretty much locked down, but I think they're still working on final drafts at the moment. |access-date= 2015-08-17 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>同一時間，莫納漢完成了他的初稿，但尚未決定導演。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.scifi.com/scifiwire/art-main.html?2003-07/16/12.00.film | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030727122942/http://www.scifi.com/scifiwire/art-main.html?2003-07%2F16%2F12.00.film | archivedate=2003-07-27 | title=''Jurassic IV'' Draft Done | publisher=Sci Fi Wire | date=2003-07-13 | accessdate=2007-02-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>與以前不同，這次故事的地點不再是熱帶叢林。同時，尼爾證實了他將會重新出演以前的角色。新電影將於2004年在[[加州|加州]]及[[夏威夷|夏威夷]]開拍。<ref>{{cite news | first=Paul | last=Davidson | url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/428/428371p1.html | title=Sam Neill Confirms ''Jurassic Park IV'' | publisher=IGN.com | date=11-07-2003 | accessdate=2007-02-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061208032702/http://movies.ign.com/articles/428/428371p1.html | archive-date=2006-12-08 | dead-url=no }}</ref>2003年9月及10月，演員[[李察·艾登布祿|李察·艾登布祿]]及古生物學家{{link-en|傑克·霍納（古生物學家）|Jack Horner (paleontologist)|傑克·霍納}}先後答應重回他們的崗位：前者繼續飾演約翰·哈蒙德，後者則仍為幕後的生物學顧問。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.aintitcool.com/display.cgi?id=16139 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20040401221637/http://www.aintitcool.com/display.cgi?id=16139 |title= Jurass Park Quattro – Guess who will be back! |publisher= AintItCool.com |date= 2003-09-19 |archivedate= 2004-04-01 |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= no }}</ref>其中，霍納還暗示[[迅猛龍|迅猛龍]]將會是新劇中的亮點之一。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.billingsgazette.com/index.php?id=1&display=rednews/2003/10/12/build/local/45-horner.inc |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20031026100309/http://www.billingsgazette.com/index.php?id=1&display=rednews%2F2003%2F10%2F12%2Fbuild%2Flocal%2F45-horner.inc |title= Scientist Horner challenges youths |work= Billings Gazette |date= 12-10-2003 |archivedate= 2003-10-26 |access-date= 2018-08-30 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>電影小組曾向他詢問有關人類演化史的新假說，看看是否能加入劇情當中。這個理論認為人是從恐龍而非哺乳動物演化而來。他當時回應說：「我還在思考，答案會在幾年後的《侏羅紀公園4》中分曉！」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dansjp3page.com/index2.asp|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20031207155508/http://dansjp3page.com/index2.asp|title=Horner Says JP4 Will Have Dino-People?!|website=DansJP3Page.com|date=2003-10-19|archivedate=2003-12-07|access-date=2015-08-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2003年底，姬拉·麗莉的角色已被設定好。<ref name=DH>{{cite web |url= http://www.darkhorizons.com/news/690/two-jurassic-4-reports |title= Two Jurassic 4 Reports |publisher= DarkHorizons.com citing ''Cinemania'' |date= 01-07-2004 |accessdate= 01-11-2014 |first= Garth |last= Franklin |quote= ...it appears Keira Knightley's potential character was written out late last year, but producers are now courting ''The Day After Tomorrow'' cutie Emmy Rossum and ''Runaway Jury'''s Jeremy Piven for two of the lead roles. |archive-url= https://archive.is/20140924043602/http://www.darkhorizons.com/news/690/two-jurassic-4-reports |archive-date= 2014-09-24 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>

翌年3月，溫斯頓表示他並沒有獲邀擔任導演，但他希望史匹堡能擔任。他還透露，新故事的發展方向與舊有的截然不同——「沒有小島、沒有暴龍、沒有舊有的一切」。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.joblo.com/index.php?id=3720 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20040304190014/http://www.joblo.com/index.php?id=3720 |title= INT: Joe Johnston |publisher= Joblo.com |date= 2004-03-03 |archivedate= 2004-03-04 |first= Thomas |last= Chau |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= no }}</ref>同年5月，{{link-en|約翰·塞爾斯|John Sayles}}接任編劇一職<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.darkhorizons.com/news/486/news-bites-wednesday-may-12th-2004 |title= News Bites: Wednesday, May 12th 2004 |publisher= DarkHorizons.com |date= 12-05-2004 |accessdate= 01-11-2014 |first= Garth |last= Franklin |archive-url= https://archive.is/20140924043543/http://www.darkhorizons.com/news/486/news-bites-wednesday-may-12th-2004 |archive-date= 2014-09-24 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>，因為莫納漢離職去編寫《[[天國驕雄|-{zh:天國驕雄; zh-hans:天国王朝; zh-hk:天國驕雄; zh-mo:天國驕雄; zh-tw:王者天下}-]]》的劇本<ref>{{cite web |url= http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2007-02-15-screenwriters-monahan_x.htm |title= William Monahan: His 'Departed' left Hong Kong for the USA |work= USA Today |date= 05-03-2007 |accessdate= 01-11-2014 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160318094950/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2007-02-15-screenwriters-monahan_x.htm |archive-date= 2016-03-18 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2004年6月，[[法蘭克·馬歇爾|法蘭克·馬歇爾]]加入監製的行列。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0550881/ |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20040619112350/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0550881/ |title= Frank Marshall IMDb page |archivedate= 2004-06-19 |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= no }}</ref>到了6月，有報導指[[亞歷士·普羅亞斯|亞歷士·普羅亞斯]]為導演的候選人，而電影會於2005年3月開拍，上映時間為該年的冬季。攝影組將首先到{{link-en|松木製片廠|Pinewood Studios}}取景，因為那裡有大水缸可用於製作海洋爬行動物一幕。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://comingsoon.net/news/jurassicpark4news.php?id=5359 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20040805060252/http://comingsoon.net/news/jurassicpark4news.php?id=5359 |title= Jurassic Park 4 Spy Report |publisher= ComingSoon.net |date= 2004-06-29 |archivedate= 2004-08-05 |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/06/29/who-might-direct-jurassic-park-iv |title= Who Might Direct Jurassic Park IV? |publisher= IGN.com |date= 2004-06-29 |accessdate= 01-11-2014 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141102011048/http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/06/29/who-might-direct-jurassic-park-iv |archive-date= 2014-11-02 |dead-url= no }}</ref>到了7月，劇本被重寫，[[傑里米·皮文|傑里米·皮文]]及[[艾美·羅森|艾美·羅森]]為新的男女主角，李察·艾登布祿則繼續扮演他以前的角色。<ref name= DH/>到了月底，普羅亞斯表示無意擔任導演。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.moviehole.net/news/3962.html |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20040808081206/http://www.moviehole.net/news/3962.html |title= Proyas on that Jurassic Park rumour |publisher= MovieHole.com |date= 2004-07-19 |archivedate= 2004-08-08 |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>8月，{{link-en|不是很酷嗎新聞網|Ain't It Cool News}}引述了一篇疑似是洩漏的劇本文章，新角色尼克·哈里斯首次亮相。劇中，他被一間瑞士公司安排負責訓練一群[[恐爪龍|恐爪龍]]進行搜救行動，而約翰·哈蒙德是唯一的原有角色。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.aintitcool.com/display.cgi?id=18166 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20050206193332/http://www.aintitcool.com/display.cgi?id=18166 |title= AICN Exclusive!! Moriarty's Been to 'Jurassic Park 4' and Returns to Tell the Tale!! |publisher= AintItCool.com |date= 2004-08-17 |archivedate= 2005-02-06 |first=  |last= Moriarty |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= https://dl.dropbox.com/u/27652498/saylesJP4script.pdf |title= Jurassic Park IV shooting script (first draft by John Sayles) |accessdate= 01-11-2014 }}{{Dead link|date=2018年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>次年，塞爾斯證實了這篇稿子的內容，並指這是駭客從他寄給史匹堡的一封電郵中盜取的。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://observer.com/2005/05/sayles-people/ |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140923154809/http://observer.com/2005/05/sayles-people/ |title= Sayles' people |work= The New York Observer |date= 2005-05-30 |archivedate= 2014-09-23 |first= Jessica |last= Bruder |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= no }}</ref>截至2004年9月，塞爾斯仍在努力編寫劇本，力求能讓電影於次年冬季如期上映。<ref>{{cite news | first=Paul | last=Davidson | url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/549/549150p1.html | title=Rewriting ''Jurassic Park IV'' | publisher=IGN | date=2004-09-17 | accessdate=2007-02-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070309143712/http://movies.ign.com/articles/549/549150p1.html | archive-date=2007-03-09 | dead-url=no }}</ref>他最終放棄了原先有關人類-恐龍基因混合生物的構思。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://collider.com/jurassic-park-4-concept-art/|title= Check out the Humanosaurus Concept Art for Scrapped Jurassic Park 4 Script|website= Collider|date= 12-10-2012|accessdate= 2014-11-29|first= Matt|last= Goldberg|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141130105841/http://collider.com/jurassic-park-4-concept-art|archive-date= 2014-11-30|dead-url= no}}</ref>2004年8月底，[[大衛·伯瑞納|大衛·伯瑞納]]獲安排演出男主角<ref>{{cite web |url= http://comingsoon.net/news/topnews.php?id=6039 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20040821155642/http://comingsoon.net/news/topnews.php?id=6039 |title= Boreanaz on Angel Movie & New Project |publisher= ComingSoon.net |date= 2004-08-18 |archivedate= 2004-08-21 |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.darkhorizons.com/news/885/sequel-rumours-galore |title= Sequel Rumours Galore |publisher= DarkHorizons.com |date= 2004-08-25 |accessdate= 01-11-2014 |first= Garth |last= Franklin |archive-url= https://archive.is/20140924043604/http://www.darkhorizons.com/news/885/sequel-rumours-galore |archive-date= 2014-09-24 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>，但他同時在考慮《[[神奇四俠|神奇四俠]]》電影組的邀請<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.moviehole.net/news/4210.html |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20040911082356/http://www.moviehole.net/news/4210.html |title= Clint in Hollywood : Angel in tights? |publisher= MovieHole.net |date= 10-09-2004 |archivedate= 2004-09-11 |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。

2005年4月，溫斯頓宣佈延遲電影的拍攝工作，因為修改多次的劇本仍不達史匹堡的標準。溫斯頓稱：「他覺得所有的版本都無法在科學與冒險元素之間取得平衡。要雙方妥協是一項艱鉅的任務：太多的科學概念會使整部電影顯得羅嗦，但過多的冒險內容又會使其顯得空虛。」<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.ign.com/articles/2005/04/12/status-of-jurassic-park-iv|title= Status of Jurassic Park IV|publisher= IGN.com|date= 11-04-2005|accessdate= 01-11-2014|first= Paul|last= Davidson|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141102021242/http://www.ign.com/articles/2005/04/12/status-of-jurassic-park-iv|archive-date= 2014-11-02|dead-url= no}}</ref>同年11月，史匹堡表示他加入了《[[侏羅紀公園2：失落的世界|迷失世界]]》小說中，男子騎著摩托車追趕迅猛龍的橋段。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.aintitcool.com/display.cgi?id=21804|title= Spielberg speaks at USC! Updates on Indy 4, Jurassic Park 4 and a remake of one of his own films!!!|website= www.AintItCool.com|date= 10-11-2005|accessdate= 09-12-2014|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080423095143/http://www.aintitcool.com/display.cgi?id=21804|archive-date= 2008-04-23|dead-url= no}}</ref>

2006年1月，約翰斯頓和霍納共同為新的劇本而努力。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.aintitcool.com/node/22323 |title= Jack Horner on the state of JURASSIC PARK 4!!! |publisher= AintItCool.com |date= 2006-01-28 |accessdate= 01-11-2014 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141102013432/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/22323 |archive-date= 2014-11-02 |dead-url= no }}</ref>一個月後，弗蘭克·馬歇爾稱新電影已有了讓人滿意的劇本初稿，並將在2007年開拍，2008年上映。<ref>{{cite news | author=Paul Davidson | url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/690/690254p1.html | title=''Jurassic Park IV'' Script Ready | publisher=IGN | date=2006-02-21 | accessdate=2007-02-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061207174605/http://movies.ign.com/articles/690/690254p1.html | archive-date=2006-12-07 | dead-url=no }}</ref>到了3月，他表示這部作品正在尋找它的導演，而約翰斯頓為人選之一。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1525628/03082006/story.jhtml |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060415045236/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1525628/03082006/story.jhtml |title=Movie File: Samaire Armstrong, Zach Braff, 'Jurassic 4,' LL Cool J, 'Casino Royale' & More |publisher=MTV |date=09-03-2006 |archivedate=2006-04-15 |first=Samaire |last=Armstrong |access-date=2015-08-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>4月，馬歇爾否認了原著小說的作者米高·克賴頓會幫忙編寫劇本，亦否認了史匹堡會擔任導演的傳聞。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.empireonline.com/interviews_and_events/interview.asp?IID=510 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20060708163013/http://www.empireonline.com/interviews_and_events/interview.asp?IID=510 |title= Frank Marshall On Eight Below, Indy IV and Jurassic Park |work= ''Empire'' |date= 2006 |archivedate= 2006-07-08 |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= no }}</ref>到了6月，劇本仍未被完成。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.boxofficemojo.com/features/?id=2099&p=.htm |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20060813133927/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/features/?id=2099&p=.htm |title= Interview: Producer and Director Frank Marshall |publisher= BoxOfficeMojo.com |date= 2006-01-24 |archivedate= 2006-08-13 |first= Scott |last= Holleran |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= no }}</ref>7月，史匹堡否認網絡上有關布雷克艾斯納擔任導演的消息，並指約翰斯頓已準備好隨時擔任導演。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.spielbergfilms.com/general/972 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20060719025101/http://www.spielbergfilms.com/general/972 |title= SpielbergFilms interviews Steven Spielberg |publisher= SpielbergFilms.com |date= 2006-07-16 |archivedate= 2006-07-19 |first= Steven, ed. |last= Awalt |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>12月，[[蘿拉·鄧恩|蘿拉·鄧恩]]指她願意重新演出她的角色，惟電影劇組沒有正式邀請她。<ref>{{cite video |url= http://www.ign.com/videos/2006/12/13/inland-empire-movie-interview-laura-dern |title= Laura Dern |time= 4:01 |publisher= IGN.com |date= 2006-12-13 |accessdate= 01-11-2014 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130615072243/http://www.ign.com/videos/2006/12/13/inland-empire-movie-interview-laura-dern |archivedate= 2013-06-15 |deadurl= no }}</ref>

2007年3月，尼爾稱他對於新電影一無所知<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.dailynews.com/celebrities/ci_5379532 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20070319041514/http://www.dailynews.com/celebrities/ci_5379532 |title= Sam Neill debunks web rumors about Jurassic Park IV |work= Los Angeles Daily News |date= 07-03-2007 |archivedate= 2007-03-19 |first1= Marilyn |last1= Beck |first2= Stacy |last2= Jenel Smith |access-date= 2015-08-18 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>，而鄧恩亦於一個月後表示工作人員沒有找她演出任何角色<ref>{{cite news | title='Jurassic Park IV' News | publisher=Collider.com | date=05-04-2007 | url=http://www.collider.com/entertainment/news/article.asp/aid/4039/tcid/1 | archivedate=2014-08-10 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810200257/http://collider.com/movie/article.asp/aid/4039/tcid/1 | deadurl=yes | access-date=2015-08-18 }}</ref>。與此同時，有報導指約翰斯頓不會擔任導演。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.mtv.com/news/1556604/jurassic-park-iv-to-hit-theaters-in-2008/ |title= 'Jurassic Park IV' To Hit Theaters In 2008 |publisher= MTV |date= 06-04-2007 |accessdate= 01-11-2014 |first= Shawn |last= Adler |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141125050535/http://www.mtv.com/news/1556604/jurassic-park-iv-to-hit-theaters-in-2008/ |archive-date= 2014-11-25 |dead-url= no }}</ref>12月，弗蘭克·馬歇爾稱進一步的劇本編寫工作需在[[2007年－2008年美國編劇協會大罷工|2007年－2008年美國編劇協會大罷工]]結束後才能開始，拍攝工作及上映時間亦會分別延遲至2008年及2009年的暑假。傑克·霍納原計劃將他於2009年出版的《如何製造一頭恐龍》一書與電影一起推出，作為一本解釋電影背後之科學理論的姐妹作品。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://beta.smithsonianmag.com/science-nature/why-do-we-keep-going-back-to-jurassic-park-117247927/?no-ist|title= Why Do We Keep Going Back to Jurassic Park?|work= ''Smithsonian''|date= 2011-10-25|accessdate= 01-11-2014|first= Brian|last= Switek|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141102015455/http://beta.smithsonianmag.com/science-nature/why-do-we-keep-going-back-to-jurassic-park-117247927/?no-ist|archive-date= 2014-11-02|dead-url= yes}}</ref>

到了2008年12月，被問道是否會繼續製作新電影，凱斯琳·甘迺迪回應道：「不，我不清楚。麥可·克萊頓去世後，我開始覺得或許我們應該到此為止，我們不應該搞砸這個系列。」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=51101|author=Silas Lenick|title=Producers Say No to Jurassic Park 4|work=ComingSoon.net|date=07-12-2008|accessdate=08-12-2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208183752/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=51101|archive-date=2008-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖然凱斯琳·甘迺迪與弗蘭克·馬歇爾不再與[[環球影業|環球影業]]簽約監製一職，但他們仍會在製片廠幫忙。<ref>{{cite journal | last1=Fernandez | first1=Jay A. | last2=Kit | first2=Borys | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3idc160e735d514c2dc69dde424ffdbab4 | title=Par, Uni won't renew major producer deals | journal=The Hollywood Reporter | date=08-12-2008 | accessdate=10-12-2008 | author= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081209004637/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3idc160e735d514c2dc69dde424ffdbab4 | archive-date=2008-12-09 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2009年11月及2010年1月，喬·約翰斯頓再一次表示《侏羅紀公園4》將會與前集截然不同，並會開創整個系列中，另一套三部曲電影。<ref>{{cite web |title=Harry claws to learn from Joe Johnston on 'Wolfman' set!!! |date=2009-11-06 |publisher=AintItCool.com |url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/42999 |accessdate=2014-11-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025144133/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/42999 |archivedate=2013-10-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=A Heap of DNA Discovered, New 'Jurassic Park' Trilogy in the Works|url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/18702/|publisher=Bloody Disgusting|access-date=2015-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020195453/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/18702/|archive-date=2014-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.collider.com/2010/01/13/director-joe-johnston-talks-captain-america-jurassic-park-4/ |title=Director Joe Johnston Talks 'Captain America', 'Jurassic Park 4' |first=Jackson |last=Cresswell |date=2010-01-13 |publisher=Collider.com |accessdate=2010-01-13 |archivedate=2013-10-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002172933/http://collider.com/director-joe-johnston-talks-captain-america-jurassic-park-4/ |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://screenrant.com/joe-johnston-jurassic-park-4-captain-america-director-rothc-123898 |title= Captain America Director Talks Jurassic Park 4 |date= 2011-07-17 |publisher= ScreenRant.com |first= Roth |last= Cornet |accessdate= 2014-11-20 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140116125816/http://screenrant.com/joe-johnston-jurassic-park-4-captain-america-director-rothc-123898/ |archivedate= 2014-01-16 |deadurl= yes }}</ref>

2011年6月15日，史匹堡兩次會晤作家馬克，希望他能修改電影的內容。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/steven-spielberg-brainstorming-jurassic-park-200911 | work=The Hollywood Reporter | first=Jay A. | last=Fernandez | title=Steven Spielberg Brainstorming 'Jurassic Park 4' with Writer Mark Protosevich (Exclusive) | date=2011-06-15 | access-date=2015-08-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150124031444/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/steven-spielberg-brainstorming-jurassic-park-200911 | archive-date=2015-01-24 | dead-url=no }}</ref>大約在一個月之後的[[聖地牙哥國際動漫展|-{zh:聖地牙哥國際動漫展; zh-hans:圣迭戈国际动漫展; zh-hk:聖地牙哥國際動漫展; zh-mo:聖地牙哥國際動漫展; zh-tw:聖地牙哥國際動漫展}-]]上，史匹堡稱有一位作家正幫忙修改劇本，電影亦會在「未來的兩、三年內」上映。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/118/1183693p1.html|title=Comic-Con: Spielberg Confirms Jurassic Park 4|first=Phil|last=Pirrello|accessdate=2011-07-22|date=2011-07-22|publisher=IGN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111216205513/http://movies.ign.com/articles/118/1183693p1.html|archive-date=2011-12-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>環球影業的代表提出了2013年為期限。<ref name="Steven Spielberg Says Jurassic Park 4 May Happen in 2 or 3 Years">{{cite news | title = Steven Spielberg Says Jurassic Park 4 May Happen in 2 or 3 Years | work = Deadline.com | date = 2011-07-22 | url = http://www.deadline.com/2011/07/steven-spielberg-says-jurassic-park-4-may-happen-in-2-to-3-years/ | accessdate = 2011-07-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110925085710/http://www.deadline.com/2011/07/steven-spielberg-says-jurassic-park-4-may-happen-in-2-to-3-years/ | archive-date = 2011-09-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>接着的三個月種，馬克為電影寫了兩個修改方案。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thisisinfamous.com/talking-oldboy-mark-protosevich-nycc/|title=Talking OLDBOY With Mark Protosevich at NYCC|first=Dan|last=Porsa|website=This is Infamous|date=2013-10-16|accessdate=2014-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141106194503/http://thisisinfamous.com/talking-oldboy-mark-protosevich-nycc/|archive-date=2014-11-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>史匹堡期望能有作家擔任電影的總編劇，並能和他另一部作品《[[林肯_(2012年電影)|林肯]]》的編制工作於2011年10月之內同時完工。可惜，他與凱斯琳·甘迺迪均認為馬克的方案未能為新電影找到正確的新方向。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.denofgeek.us/movies/18590/kathleen-kennedy-interview-war-horse-lincoln-studio-ghibli-jurassic-park-4-more |title=Kathleen Kennedy interview: War Horse, Lincoln, Studio Ghibli, Jurassic Park 4 & more |first=Michael |last=Leader |publisher=Den of Geek |date=12-01-2012 |accessdate=2014-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705083203/http://www.denofgeek.us/movies/18590/kathleen-kennedy-interview-war-horse-lincoln-studio-ghibli-jurassic-park-4-more |archive-date=2015-07-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過，到了10月，他證實馬克仍在編寫劇本，而這次的故事情節要比《侏羅紀公園3》更佳。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=32315|title=Spielberg: More Indy & Jurassic Park?|website=Empire|accessdate=02-04-2012|date=2011-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120512003550/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=32315|archive-date=2012-05-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年1月，史匹堡再次表示他不會任導演，但會擔任製片人。同年6月21日，編劇塵埃落定，是《[[猩球崛起|猩球崛起]]》的作者{{link-en|瑞克·傑法與亞曼達·賽佛|Rick Jaffa and Amanda Silver}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://collider.com/jurassic-park-4-sequel-rick-jaffa-amanda-silver/174765/ |title='Rise of the Planet of the Apes' Writers Rick Jaffa and Amanda Silver to Script 'Jurassic Park 4 |first=Brendan |last=Bettinger |date=n.d. |archivedate=2013-03-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130304212801/http://collider.com/jurassic-park-4-sequel-rick-jaffa-amanda-silver/ |deadurl=no |publisher=Collider.com |accessdate=2013-08-20 }}</ref>

