2013年1月11日，[[環球影業|環球影業]]表示電影會以[[3D電影|三維模式]]於2014年6月13日上映。<ref name="releasedate1">{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/01/jurassic-park-4-release-june-13-2014-steven-spielberg|title=Breaking: Universal Sets Date for 'Jurassic Park 4'|publisher=Deadline.com|date=11-01-2013|accessdate=2013-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130126070919/http://www.deadline.com/2013/01/jurassic-park-4-release-june-13-2014-steven-spielberg/|archive-date=2013-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>到了2月，[[凱斯琳·甘迺迪_(電影監製)|凱斯琳·甘迺迪]]宣佈不再擔任此片的製作人，因為她希望能專注於將在2015年上映的《[[星球大戰七部曲：原力覺醒|-{zh:星球大戰七部曲：原力覺醒; zh-hans:星球大战VII：原力觉醒; zh-hk:星球大戰七部曲：原力覺醒; zh-mo:星球大戰七部曲：原力覺醒; zh-tw:星際大戰七部曲：原力覺醒}-]]》的工作上。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://filmonic.com/kathleen-kennedy-will-not-produce-jurassic-park-iv-instead-focusing-on-star-wars|title=Kathleen Kennedy will not produce Jurassic Park IV; Instead focusing on Star Wars|work=Filmonic|accessdate=2013-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019135333/http://filmonic.com/kathleen-kennedy-will-not-produce-jurassic-park-iv-instead-focusing-on-star-wars|archive-date=2013-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>另一製作人[[弗蘭克·馬歇爾|弗蘭克·馬歇爾]]說：「我們尚未決定在哪裡展開拍攝工作。」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/LeDoctor/status/305047093918191616 |title=No decisions have been made regarding where we are shooting. |author=Frank Marshall |publisher=Twitter.com |accessdate=2013-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131006171600/https://twitter.com/LeDoctor/status/305047093918191616 |archive-date=2013-10-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>過了不久，位於[[巴吞魯日_(路易斯安那州)|巴吞魯日]]的{{link-en|著名播放器電影公司|Famous Players Film Company|羅利攝製室}}表示，環球影業已經預約了他們的場地，使用期為2013年的4至11月，但沒有指明這是用於什麼電影。<ref name="NOLA">{{cite web | title = 'Jurassic Park 4' to shoot in Baton Rouge? Universal appears to be eyeballing city for high-profile sequel | first = Mike | last = Scott | work = The Times-Picayune | location = New Orleans, Louisiana | date = 12-03-2013 | url = http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2013/03/jurassic_park_4_to_shoot_in_ba.html | accessdate = 2013-03-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130317001612/http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2013/03/jurassic_park_4_to_shoot_in_ba.html | archive-date = 2013-03-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>同年4月13日，發佈商宣佈《[[安全無保障|安全無保障]]》的導演[[柯林·特雷沃羅|柯林·特雷沃羅]]將出任本片的導演一職<ref name="director1">{{cite web|title=Jurassic Park 4 Gets a Director (Hint: It's Not Steven Spielberg)|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/397898/jurassic-park-4-gets-a-director-hint-it-s-not-steven-spielberg|first=Natalie|last=Finn|date=2013-03-14|publisher=E! Online|accessdate=2013-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130317125042/http://www.eonline.com/news/397898/jurassic-park-4-gets-a-director-hint-it-s-not-steven-spielberg|archive-date=2013-03-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="director2">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-21798898 |title=Jurassic Park 4 to be directed by Colin Trevorrow |publisher=BBC |date=2013-03-15 |accessdate=2013-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130507202339/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-21798898 |archive-date=2013-05-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而帕特里克·克勞利則為製作人<ref name="IFC">{{cite web | title=Colin Trevorrow to Direct 'Jurassic Park 4' | first=Jordan | last=Zakarin | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/colin-trevorrow-direct-jurassic-park-428696 | work=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2013-03-14 | accessdate=2014-11-25 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109072611/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/colin-trevorrow-direct-jurassic-park-428696 | archivedate=2014-01-09 | deadurl=no }}</ref>。

特雷沃羅之所以成為導演與另一部電影有關。忙於執導《[[明日世界_(電影)|明日世界]]》的[[畢·貝特|畢·貝特]]有意出任《-{zh:星球大戰七部曲：原力覺醒; zh-hans:星球大战VII：原力觉醒; zh-hk:星球大戰七部曲：原力覺醒; zh-mo:星球大戰七部曲：原力覺醒; zh-tw:星際大戰七部曲：原力覺醒}-》的導演一職。為解決時間上的衝突，他曾向凱斯琳·甘迺迪建議讓特雷沃羅先代替他處理《星球大戰》的職務，直到《明日世界》的錄製工作結束。雖然這一系列的計劃都未能實現，但凱斯琳·甘迺迪及弗蘭克·馬歇爾兩夫婦因而觀看了《安全無保障》，並留下了深刻印象。<ref name=April28>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/jurassic-world-star-wars/|title=How Brad Bird Almost Helming 'Star Wars' Resulted in Colin Trevorrow Directing 'Jurassic World'|website=Slashfilm.com|date=2015-04-28|accessdate=2015-04-30|first=Peter|last=Sciretta|page=1{{ndash}}2|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150430144401/http://www.slashfilm.com/jurassic-world-star-wars|archive-date=2015-04-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>馬歇爾馬上安排了特雷沃羅與史匹堡會面，特雷沃羅還沒來得及閱讀當時正由傑法與賽佛編寫的劇本，就已經獲聘請。<ref name=April30>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/colin-trevorrow-jurassic-world-interview/|title=Extensive Jurassic World Interview with Director Colin Trevorrow|website=Slashfilm.com|date=2015-04-30|accessdate=2015-04-30|first=Peter|last=Sciretta|page=1{{ndash}}3|archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20150702094024/http://www.slashfilm.com/colin%2Dtrevorrow%2Djurassic%2Dworld%2Dinterview/|archive-date=2015-07-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

傑法與賽佛筆下的故事仍圍繞著主題樂園並在中國展開，先前由塞爾斯構思的[[迅猛龍|迅猛龍]]馴服計劃也在史匹堡的支持下獲得保留。<ref name=Empire1>{{cite news|last=de Semlyen|first=Nick|date=2015-04-30|title=''Jurassic World'' set visit|newspaper=Empire|location=U.K.|quote=Trevorrow was asked to cook up his own story. But there were a couple of concepts that he wanted to keep. One was Sayles' audacious notion of raptors working alongside humans. "Dinosaurs hunting down drug lords? I couldn't go there," he says. "But I could rewind all the way back and make a movie about the very tenuous relationship between man and a vicious animal. [...] The other very cool idea, which came from Spielberg himself: what if John Hammond's dream of a fully functioning dinosaur theme park came true?"|page=82}}</ref><ref name=Empire2>{{cite news|last=de Semlyen|first=Nick|date=2015-04-30|title=''Jurassic World'' set visit|newspaper=Empire |location=U.K.|quote=In 2007 [''sic''], news broke of a Jurassic Park 4 script by American indie king John Sayles, in which trained raptors take on a drug baron's army. The project stalled, but this nucleus of an idea stuck around, making its way into the next commissioned draft, by Rise Of The Planet Of The Apes' Rick Jaffa and Amanda Silver. And this is where Colin Trevorrow, the man chosen to head up Jurassic World, comes in. [...] One can only imagine how excited he was to be presented with the latest script by the threequel's producers. He sat down to read it. Flipped through every page. Then said thanks, but no thanks. "It was as difficult to decline as you'd think," he recalls. "But I knew I couldn't make that film. So I said, 'I'm honoured, but if we're going to do this we really need to build a different movie that can also be called Jurassic Park 4."|page=81{{ndash}}82}}</ref><ref name=Marshall/>這個版本中的兇王龍為以前聞所未聞的新種恐龍，而非後來設定的基因混合動物。<ref name=Marshall>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/frank-marshall-interview/2/|title=Interview: Producer Frank Marshall Talks 'Jurassic World,' 'Indiana Jones 5,' and 'Back to the Future'|website=SlashFilm|date=2015-06-19|access-date=2015-07-07|first=Peter|last=Sciretta|page=2{{ndash}}3|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150822180705/http://www.slashfilm.com/frank-marshall-interview/2/|archive-date=2015-08-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>

可是，特雷沃羅在細讀文本後拒絕執導，除非更改劇情。他自己有了新的主意，並與夥伴{{link-en|德瑞克·康納利|Derek Connolly}}著手編寫新的版本。<ref name="Trevorrow_interview" /><ref name="hollywoodreporter-filmonhold" />他們仍以恐龍樂園作故事的主題，並保留了恐龍逃脫及人類馴服迅猛龍這兩個部分。<ref name=April30/><ref name=Empire1/>只不過，特雷沃羅認為原先的版本過於誇張，需要「收回來」。<ref name=Empire1/>他採用了基因混合恐龍的設定，以乎合《侏羅紀公園系列》作品一貫的做法——尊重及緊貼最新的古生物學知識。他表示：「我不想告訴小孩一種還未被發現的恐龍是真實存在的。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/videos/2015/07/05/whats-it-like-to-have-a-job-interview-with-steven-spielberg|title=What's It Like to Have a Job Interview with Steven Spielberg?|website=IGN|time=4:14|date=05-07-2015|access-date=2015-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706054800/http://www.ign.com/videos/2015/07/05/whats-it-like-to-have-a-job-interview-with-steven-spielberg|archive-date=2015-07-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年4月，傑克·霍納在一次的訪問中透露：「一種嶄新的恐龍將會登場。我暫時不能告訴你們這具體是什麼，但你們一定會期待牠的出現！」<ref>{{cite news | title=20 years later, 'Jurassic Park' reopens in 3-D | url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/04/03/jurassic-park-3d/1996081/ | first=Bryan | last=Alexander | work=USA Today | date=03-04-2013 | accessdate=2014-01-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131228144330/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/04/03/jurassic-park-3d/1996081/ | archive-date=2013-12-28 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

特雷沃羅與康納利花了數週改寫劇本。<ref name=April30/>製作室於2013年5月6日收到了稿子，並發現內容比預期改變了更多。<ref name="hollywoodreporter-filmonhold" />2013年5月8日，他們宣佈電影會延遲上映，但並沒有給予具體的日子。<ref>{{cite journal |title=Universal delays 'Jurassic Park 4' release |author=Justin Kroll |url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/universal-delays-jurassic-park-4-release-1200477065/ |magazine=Variety |date=08-05-2013 |accessdate=10-05-2013 |journal= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510113918/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/universal-delays-jurassic-park-4-release-1200477065/ |archive-date=2013-05-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title='Jurassic Park 4' release date put on hold in order to 'bring audiences the best possible version' |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/jurassic-park-2014-release-put-hold-order-bring-audiences-best-version-article-1.1338673#ixzz2SpkeqYhd |newspaper=Daily News |location=New York City |date=08-05-2013 |accessdate=10-05-2013 |agency=Reuters |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510142121/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/jurassic-park-2014-release-put-hold-order-bring-audiences-best-version-article-1.1338673#ixzz2SpkeqYhd |archive-date=2013-05-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在此之前，[[拜絲·黛麗·侯活|拜絲·黛麗·侯活]]、[[大衛·奧伊羅|大衛·奧伊羅]]、[[加烈·希隆|加烈·希隆]]三位演員已獲加入演員候選名單。<ref name=WorldDate/>電影開拍日被定為2013年6月24日。<ref name="hollywoodreporter-filmonhold">{{cite news |first=Borys |last=Kit |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/jurassic-park-4-universal-puts-519479 |title='Jurassic Park 4': Universal Puts Film on Hold |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=08-05-2013 |accessdate=11-09-2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130907095016/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/jurassic-park-4-universal-puts-519479 |archive-date=2013-09-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>延遲上映使特雷沃羅與康納利有了更多時間完善劇本<ref name="Trevorrow_interview"/>，也使製作人員有更多時間設置這個虛構樂園的場景（他們本打算以電腦特技製作）<ref name=April30/>。

2013年5月，特雷沃羅在實地考察時拍下了一幀[[考艾島|考艾島]]的照片，並在 [[Twitter|Twitter]] 上以「努布拉島」（第一部電影中的事發地點）一稱發佈。<ref name="collider.com">{{cite web|title=Does 'Jurassic Park 4' Take Place on the Original Island Isla Nublar?|url=http://collider.com/jurassic-park-4-island-nublar/|accessdate=2013-05-05|publisher=Collider.com|first=Adam|last=Chitwood|date=n.d.|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130505004828/http://collider.com/jurassic-park-4-island-nublar/|archivedate=2013-05-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>同年6月1日，他保證：「電影一定會面世。我們正全力編寫及設計它。」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/colintrevorrow/status/340993309671579649 |title=@JurassicPark14 No, very much |publisher=Twitter.com |accessdate=2013-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131026043053/https://twitter.com/colintrevorrow/status/340993309671579649 |archive-date=2013-10-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>11月，他亦在 Twitter 上稱：「『重啟』會是最好的詞語——新故事會在侏羅紀公園事件22年後展開。」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/colintrevorrow/statuses/404292212596670464 |title=Reboot is a strong word |publisher=Colin Trevorrow @colintrevorrow at Twitter.com |date=2013-11-23 |accessdate=2014-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412052144/https://twitter.com/colintrevorrow/statuses/404292212596670464 |archive-date=2014-04-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>根據他的說法，電影將於2015年呈現給觀眾。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/jurassic-park-4-rumors-colin-trevorrow/|title=Director Colin Trevorrow Addresses 'Jurassic Park 4'  Rumors; Says He Needs to Make a Case for 'Why the Hell There's a JP4 in the First Place'|first=Adam|last=Chitwood|publisher=Collider.com|date=2013-08-15|accessdate=2013-08-20|archivedate=2013-08-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130818083000/http://collider.com/jurassic-park-4-rumors-colin-trevorrow|deadurl=no}}</ref>6月18日，一幅2013年{{link-en|國際授權博覽會|Licensing International Expo}}上展示的橫額亦暗示2015年將為新作面世之日。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=105599 |title=Exclusive: Jurassic Park 4 Targeted for 2015, to be Shot in 3D |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2013-06-18 |accessdate=2013-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921162848/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=105599 |archive-date=2013-09-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>同樣在2013年5月，[[森·尼爾|森·尼爾]]表示他不會出演此劇，並指：「我被告知這將重啟整個系列，會是全新的故事。」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/dominion-post/capital-life/8689803/Sam-Neils-vintage-year |title=Sam Neil's vintage year |work=The Dominion Post |location=Wellington, New Zealand |first=James |last=Croot |date=2013-05-19 |accessdate=2013-12-17 |archivedate=2014-11-26 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6UMTSVTCE?url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/dominion-post/capital-life/8689803/Sam-Neils-vintage-year |deadurl=no }}</ref>8月15日，[[約翰·卡拉辛斯基|約翰·卡拉辛斯基]]正與電影組商量出演恐龍馴獸師的事宜。<ref>{{cite web|last=Connelly|first=Brendon|title=Rumour: John Krasinski Taking A Dinosaur Tamer Job On Jurassic Park 4?|url=http://www.bleedingcool.com/2013/08/15/rumour-john-krasinski-taking-a-dinosuar-tamer-job-on-jurassic-park-4/|publisher=Bleeding Cool|accessdate=2013-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019130301/http://www.bleedingcool.com/2013/08/15/rumour-john-krasinski-taking-a-dinosuar-tamer-job-on-jurassic-park-4/|archive-date=2013-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年暑假，特雷沃羅與康納利又對劇本進行了修改，並在9月獲批使用。<ref name="Trevorrow_interview"/>除了兇王龍之外，特雷沃羅本來還想再加入一隻名為「劍角龍」的基因混合恐龍（結合了[[劍龍|劍龍]]及[[三角龍|三角龍]]的基因），但最終在他兒子的提醒下放棄了這個構思，因為太多的基因混合恐龍將無法凸顯兇王龍的獨特性。<ref name=April30/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.empireonline.com/features/secrets-of-jurassic-world|title=Trevorrow's Son Nixed The Stegoceratops|work=Empire|date=2015-06-15|accessdate=2015-06-16|first=Phil|last=de Semlyen|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617010755/http://www.empireonline.com/features/secrets-of-jurassic-world|archive-date=2015-06-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年9月10日，環球影業宣佈新作將以「侏羅紀世界」之名於2015年6月12日上映。<ref name=WorldDate>{{cite news|last=Kroll|first=Justin|title=Universal Dates 'Jurassic Park 4′; Renames It 'Jurassic World'|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/jurassic-park-4-jurassic-world-1200606985/|accessdate=11-09-2013|newspaper=Variety|date=10-09-2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911012155/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/jurassic-park-4-jurassic-world-1200606985/|archive-date=2013-09-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>特雷沃羅沒有沿用「侏羅紀公園4」一稱，因為他希望此作能在整個系列中開闢一條新的道路。<ref>{{cite news|last=de Semlyen|first=Nick|date=2015-04-30|title=''Jurassic World'' set visit|newspaper=Empire|location=U.K.|quote="Trevorrow had a brainwave of his own. "I emailed Steven{{ndash}}one of the most carefully worded emails I've ever written{{ndash}}and explained every single reason why we should change the title from Jurassic Park 4 to Jurassic World. It's like changing the recipe of someone's favourite cereal, but I wanted people to know that this is going to be a bold movie. It's going to be different."|page=82}}</ref>同月，拜絲·黛麗·侯活正與電影組商量角色的事宜<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.thewrap.com/bryce-dallas-howard-in-early-talks-to-star-in-universals-jurassic-world-exclusive/ | title = Bryce Dallas Howard in Early Talks to Star in Universal's 'Jurassic World' (Exclusive) | publisher = TheWrap.com | first = Jeff | last = Sneider | date = 2013-11-26 | accessdate = 2013-12-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203020913/http://www.thewrap.com/bryce-dallas-howard-in-early-talks-to-star-in-universals-jurassic-world-exclusive/ | archive-date = 2013-12-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，後於11月正式出演<ref>{{cite news|last=Freydkin|first=Donna|title=Ron Howard pictures working with his daughter Bryce|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/people/2013/11/01/bryce-ron-howard-canon/3346825/|newspaper=USA Today|date=01-11-2013|access-date=2015-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109080833/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/people/2013/11/01/bryce-ron-howard-canon/3346825/|archive-date=2013-11-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月中，[[泰·辛普金斯|泰·辛普金斯]]獲安排了角色，[[傑克·約翰森|傑克·約翰森]]亦考慮出演。<ref>{{cite web | url= http://deadline.com/2013/10/ty-simpkins-lands-lead-in-jurassic-world/ | title= Ty Simpkins Lands Lead In 'Jurassic World' | first= Mike Jr. | last= Fleming | publisher= Deadline.com | date= 2013-10-14 | accessdate= 2013-12-17 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131128053912/http://www.deadline.com/2013/10/ty-simpkins-lands-lead-in-jurassic-world/ | archive-date= 2013-11-28 | dead-url= no }}</ref>[[尼克·羅賓森|尼克·羅賓森]]其後也獲安排飾演辛普金斯的兄長<ref>{{cite news | url= http://hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/jurassic-world-nabs-kings-summer-648229 | title= 'Jurassic World' Nabs 'Kings of Summer' Actor | date= 2013-10-15 | first= Borys | last= Kit | work= The Hollywood Reporter | accessdate= 2013-12-17 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140106081100/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/jurassic-world-nabs-kings-summer-648229 | archive-date= 2014-01-06 | dead-url= no }}</ref>，而[[佐斯·布連|佐斯·布連]]亦正考慮出演男主角<ref>{{cite news | url = http://variety.com/2013/film/news/josh-brolin-in-talks-to-star-in-jurassic-world-1200738454/ | title = Josh Brolin In Talks to Star in 'Jurassic World' | first = Justin | last = Kroll | work = Variety | date = 2013-10-18 | accessdate = 2013-12-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131222200508/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/josh-brolin-in-talks-to-star-in-jurassic-world-1200738454/ | archive-date = 2013-12-22 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。一個月後，布連已不在演員的候選名單上，取而代之的是[[基斯柏特|基斯柏特]]。<ref name=wrap-11-13-13>{{cite web | url= http://www.thewrap.com/chris-pratt-jurassic-world-lead-role | title= 'Guardians of the Galaxy' Star Chris Pratt Circling Lead in 'Jurassic World' (Exclusive) | first= Jeff | last= Sneider | publisher= TheWrap.com | date= 2013-11-13 | accessdate= 2013-12-17 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131128071652/http://www.thewrap.com/chris-pratt-jurassic-world-lead-role | archive-date= 2013-11-28 | dead-url= no }}</ref>[[朗·侯活|朗·-{zh:侯活;zh-cn:霍华德;zh-hk:侯活;zh-tw:霍華;}-]]於2014年1月在 Twitter 上證實，基斯柏特將飾演男主角。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://twitter.com/RealRonHoward/status/422628990751223808 | publisher = Ron Howard verified Twitter.com page | date = 2014-01-13 | accessdate = 2014-01-14 | title = Bryce and Chris meet.... | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140130155345/https://twitter.com/RealRonHoward/status/422628990751223808 | archive-date = 2014-01-30 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2014年2月5日，特雷沃羅宣佈[[約翰·施瓦茲曼|約翰·施瓦茲曼]]將擔任攝影師，以[[潘那维申|潘那维申]]製的攝影機及[[伊士曼柯達公司|柯達]]35與65毫米的膠片拍攝。<ref>{{cite web|title='Jurassic World' to be shot on 35mm and 65mm film, not digital, director reveals|url=http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2014/02/jurassic_world_to_shoot_on_35m.html|work=The Times Picayune|first=Mike|last=Scott|date=06-02-2014|accessdate=09-03-2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228011852/http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2014/02/jurassic_world_to_shoot_on_35m.html|archive-date=2014-02-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>除了考慮到施瓦茲曼與史匹堡的個人意見外，電影組選擇了以[[膠片電影|膠片]]而非[[數字電影|數字]]模式攝製是為了維持前三部電影的視覺美感，而且數字攝影機也沒有足夠的[[動態範圍|動態範圍]]去拍攝野外叢林的鏡頭。製片人需要額外的特效，故採用了65毫米的膠片用於排序視覺效果及[[外景拍攝|外景拍攝]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=ONFILM Interview: John Schwartzman, ASC|url=http://motion.kodak.com/motion/Publications/InCamera/Sections/ONFILM/ONFILM_Interview_John_Schwartzman_ASC.htm|work=Kodak ON FILM|date=2014-05-05|accessdate=03-12-2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208121351/http://motion.kodak.com/motion/Publications/InCamera/Sections/ONFILM/ONFILM_Interview_John_Schwartzman_ASC.htm|archive-date=2014-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>電影以2.00:1的[[長寬比_(影像)|長寬比]]呈現，這剛好落在1.85:1及2.35:1兩個電影業常用的寬銀幕比例標準之間。這個比例可以兼顧恐龍及人類的高度，讓他們能同時落入同一個畫面內；這也最為貼近 [[IMAX|IMAX]] 的銀幕比例。<ref>{{cite web|title=EXCLUSIVE INTERVIEW WITH THE DIRECTOR OF JURASSIC WORLD|url=http://au.ign.com/articles/2014/03/18/exclusive-interview-with-the-director-of-jurassic-world|work=IGN|date=2014-03-18|accessdate=03-12-2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518213336/http://au.ign.com/articles/2014/03/18/exclusive-interview-with-the-director-of-jurassic-world|archive-date=2015-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年2月7日，[[傳奇電影公司|傳奇電影公司]]同意提供贊助<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.honolulupulse.com/2014/02/outtakes-online-jurassic-world/ |first=Mike |last=Gordon |title=Outtakes Online: 'Jurassic World' to film in Hawaii |work=Honolulu Star-Advertiser |date=07-02-2014 |accessdate=2014-11-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221213927/http://www.honolulupulse.com/2014/02/outtakes-online-jurassic-world/ |archivedate=2014-02-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>；有報導指[[中國電影集團|中國電影集團]]亦會投放資金<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.forbes.com/sites/robcain/2015/06/12/dinos-roar-on-sino-tour/|title= "Jurassic World" Dinos Roar on Sino Tour|author= Rob Cain|date= 12-06-2015|accessdate= 2015-06-13|work= forbes.com|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150614154231/http://www.forbes.com/sites/robcain/2015/06/12/dinos-roar-on-sino-tour/|archive-date= 2015-06-14|dead-url= no}}</ref>。同月28日，[[文森特·諾費奧|文森特·諾費奧]]加入了演員行列，飾演故事中的奸角；[[伊凡·卡漢|伊凡·卡漢]]則會出演-{zh:馬斯蘭尼;zh-tw:馬斯拉尼;zh-hk:馬斯蘭尼;zh-cn:马斯拉尼;}-國際企業、侏羅紀世界的大股東。<ref name="Vincent D'Onofrio To Play Villain">{{cite web|last=Fleming, Jr.|first=Mike|title=Vincent D'Onofrio To Play Villain In 'Jurassic World'|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/vincent-donofrio-jurassic-world-villain-role/|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2014-02-28|accessdate=2014-02-28|archivedate=2014-11-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141126014302/http://deadline.com/interstitial/|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Cricket ka decline hona bhi chahiye, it is a waste of time: Irrfan Khan|url=http://www.abplive.in/video/video_movies/2014/03/12/article276317.ece/Cricket%C2%A0ka%C2%A0decline%C2%A0hona-bhi-chahiye-it-is-a-waste-of-time-Irrfan-Khan#.UyC2adyAdBW|publisher=ABP Live|accessdate=2014-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315034940/http://www.abplive.in/video/video_movies/2014/03/12/article276317.ece/Cricket%C2%A0ka%C2%A0decline%C2%A0hona-bhi-chahiye-it-is-a-waste-of-time-Irrfan-Khan#.UyC2adyAdBW|archive-date=2014-03-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>與此同時，特雷沃羅證實[[黃榮亮|黃榮亮]]將繼續扮演吳亨利博士，但這次他在劇中的重要性會更高。<ref name="Trevorrow_interview">{{cite web|title=Exclusive Interview with the Director of 'Jurassic World'|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/03/18/exclusive-interview-with-the-director-of-jurassic-world|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2014-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140319101549/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/03/18/exclusive-interview-with-the-director-of-jurassic-world|archive-date=2014-03-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月21日，[[歐馬·希|歐馬·希]]宣佈加盟侏羅紀世界。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://twitter.com/OmarSy/statuses/446904287205920768 | title=Fan of this saga from the beginning... | authorlink=Omar Sy | first=Omar | last=Sy | publisher=Twitter.com | date=2014-03-21 | accessdate=2014-03-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324173249/https://twitter.com/OmarSy/statuses/446904287205920768 | archive-date=2014-03-24 | dead-url=no }}</ref>五天後，傑克·約翰遜獲安排飾演一名技術嫻熟的操作監督員——羅瑞·庫瑟。<ref name="Jake Johnson Interview">{{cite web|last=Haynes-Peterson|first=Robert|title=Jake Johnson Interview|url=http://www.askmen.com/fine_living/wine_dine_archive/jake-johnson-beer-rules.html|publisher=AskMen.com|accessdate=2014-06-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019074059/http://www.askmen.com/fine_living/wine_dine_archive/jake-johnson-beer-rules.html|archivedate=2014-10-19|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Jake Johnson confirms role">{{cite web|last1=Heyman|first1=Jessie|title=Jake Johnson On Last Night's 'New Girl' Game Changer & Prince's Omelettes|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/03/26/jake-johnson-new-girl-breakup_n_5034606.html|website=Huffington Post|accessdate=2014-06-27|date=2014-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140905222311/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/03/26/jake-johnson-new-girl-breakup_n_5034606.html|archive-date=2014-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>4月3日，[[茱蒂·葛瑞兒|茱蒂·葛瑞兒]]、[[凱蒂·麥克格拉思|凱蒂·麥克格拉思]]、{{link-en|蘿倫·拉布庫斯|Lauren Lapkus}}都已獲安排角色。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/judy-greer-joins-jurassic-world-693459|title=Judy Greer Joins 'Jurassic World'|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=03-04-2014|accessdate=03-04-2014|first=Borys|last=Kit|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140404165506/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/judy-greer-joins-jurassic-world-693459|archive-date=2014-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{link-en|安迪·柏克利|Andy Buckley}}與詹士·杜蒙特亦分別於5月7日及6月27日確定加入演員陣營。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/the-office-actor-andy-buckley-joins-jurassic-world-exclusive-1201173484/ | title='The Office' Actor Andy Buckley Joins 'Jurassic World' (EXCLUSIVE) | first=Dave | last=McNary | date=07-05-2014 | work=Variety | accessdate=07-05-2014 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140508033021/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/the-office-actor-andy-buckley-joins-jurassic-world-exclusive-1201173484/ | archive-date=2014-05-08 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="James DuMont Joins Cast">{{cite web|last1=Siegel|first1=Tatiana|title=James DuMont Joins Cast of Universal's 'Jurassic World' (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/james-dumont-joins-cast-universals-715493|work=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2014-06-27|date=2014-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706205217/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/james-dumont-joins-cast-universals-715493|archive-date=2014-07-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===拍攝過程===
