電影於2014年4月10日正式開拍。<ref>{{cite web|url= https://twitter.com/LeDoctor/status/454453755958657024|title= JURASSIC WORLD lives! First shot: 8:20 am. All is good.|publisher= Twitter.com|date= 10-08-2014|accessdate= 01-11-2014|first= Frank|last= Marshall|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141126150039/https://twitter.com/LeDoctor/status/454453755958657024|archive-date= 2014-11-26|dead-url= no}}</ref>電影組的第一站為[[夏威夷|夏威夷]]的[[檀香山動物園|檀香山動物園]]<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2602363/Bollywood-actor-Irrfan-Khan-pictured-set-Jurassic-World-filming-kicks-Hawaii-action-movie-sequel.html|title= Bollywood actor Irrfan Khan pictured on set of Jurassic World as filming kicks off in Hawaii on action movie sequel|work= Daily Mail|location= London|date= 11-04-2014|accessdate= 01-11-2014|first= Sarah|last= Bull|archive-url= https://archive.is/20140411115223/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2602363/Bollywood-actor-Irrfan-Khan-pictured-set-Jurassic-World-filming-kicks-Hawaii-action-movie-sequel.html|archive-date= 2014-04-11|dead-url= no}}</ref>，他們在[[歐胡島|歐胡島]]停留了四週<ref name= HFVM >{{cite web|url= http://issuu.com/mipgroup/docs/hm_3-14_web/1%22|title= Jurassic World production information|website= Hawaii Film & Video Magazine [pages 11, 29 and 32]|date= 2014-09-25|accessdate= 07-11-2014|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141106010957/http://issuu.com/mipgroup/docs/hm_3-14_web/1%22|archive-date= 2014-11-06|dead-url= no}}</ref>，並在4月底到訪了[[夏威夷會議中心|夏威夷會議中心]]<ref>{{cite news|url= http://m.theepochtimes.com/n3/646885-jurassic-world-jurassic-park-4-new-hawaii-set-photos-details-about-possible-sequels/|title= Jurassic World (Jurassic Park 4): New Hawaii Set Photos, Details About Possible Sequels|newspaper= The Epoch Times|date= 2014-04-28|accessdate= 07-11-2014-|first= Zachary|last= Stieber|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141108090016/http://m.theepochtimes.com/n3/646885-jurassic-world-jurassic-park-4-new-hawaii-set-photos-details-about-possible-sequels/|archive-date= 2014-11-08|dead-url= no}}</ref>。5月15日，攝影場地轉移至[[考愛島|考愛島]]，一直到6月6日。<ref name= HFVM />其後，他們隨即轉移到已被棄置的{{link-en|新奧爾良四旗公園|Six Flags New Orleans}}<ref name= LFVM >{{cite web|url= http://issuu.com/mipgroup/docs/lm_5-14_web/1|title= Feature Films Flock to Nola's Audubon Nature Institute|website= Louisiana Film & Video Magazine [page 59]|date= 09-10-2014|accessdate= 07-11-2014|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141108083158/http://issuu.com/mipgroup/docs/lm_5-14_web/1|archive-date= 2014-11-08|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name=location>{{cite news | url = http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2014/06/02/jurassic-world-begins-filming-at-the-abandoned-six-flags-in-new-orleans-this-week/ | title = 'Jurassic World' begins filming at the abandoned Six Flags in New Orleans this week | date = 02-06-2014 | work = On Location Vacations | accessdate = 03-06-2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140604055544/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2014/06/02/jurassic-world-begins-filming-at-the-abandoned-six-flags-in-new-orleans-this-week/ | archive-date = 2014-06-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，並在那裡建立了侏羅紀世界的樂園主大道。樂園內還有一座哈蒙德的雕像，以紀念飾演他的演員[[李察·艾登布祿|李察·艾登布祿]]。<ref name=SR/><ref name=April30/>根據行程安排，電影組需要花11週在[[路易斯安娜州|路易斯安娜州]]進行拍攝工作。<ref name=location/>2014年6月30日，他們到了[[新奧爾良路易斯岩士唐國際機場|新奧爾良路易斯岩士唐國際機場]]取景。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://jurassicworld.org/index.php?id=166 | title = 'Jurassic World filming moves to Louis Armstrong International Airport! | date = 2014-06-30 | publisher = JurassicWorld.org | accessdate = 2014-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402091713/http://jurassicworld.org/index.php?id=166 | archive-date = 2015-04-02 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>劇中，遊客撤離及沼澤地的鏡頭分別取自{{link-en|奧杜邦動物園|Audubon Zoo}}及[[斯萊德爾_(路易斯安那州)|斯萊德爾]]。<ref name= LFVM />。2014年8月5日，導演特雷沃羅在 Twitter 上稱長達78天的攝影工作終於完工。<ref>{{cite news | url = https://twitter.com/colintrevorrow/status/496735900848914432 | title = Wrapped | date = 05-08-2014 | publisher = Twitter.com | accessdate = 05-08-2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140806225025/https://twitter.com/colintrevorrow/status/496735900848914432 | archive-date = 2014-08-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=June11/>

《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》報導，特雷沃羅特意請來了{{link-en|傳統特技公司|Legacy Effects}}為電影製作{{link-en|電子動畫|animatronics}}恐龍，就跟前三集一樣。<ref name=scified>{{cite news | url = http://www.scified.com/site/jurassicworld/colin-trevorrow-confirms-animatronic-dinosaurs--sequels-for-jurassic-world | title = Colin Trevorrow Confirms Animatronic Dinosaurs & Sequels for Jurassic World! | date = 2014-04-23 | work = Scified | accessdate = 2014-05-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140528034819/http://www.scified.com/site/jurassicworld/colin-trevorrow-confirms-animatronic-dinosaurs--sequels-for-jurassic-world | archive-date = 2014-05-28 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>有關公司提供了照明參考模型及供電影組在夏威夷進行序列拍攝的實體電子動畫雷龍。特效管理員{{link-en|菲爾·蒂皮特|Phil Tippett}}及[[光影魔幻工業|光影魔幻工業]]均繼續幫忙以[[動作捕捉|動作捕捉]]法（以真人模仿恐龍的動作）製作[[電腦成像|電腦成像]]恐龍。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jurassicworld-movie.com/news/1379|title=Phil Tippett reunites with ILM for visual effects on Jurassic World!|work=Scified|date=2013-12-13|accessdate=2014-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502120650/http://www.jurassicworld-movie.com/news/1379|archive-date=2014-05-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name= slashvisit >{{cite web|title=50 Things I Learned on the Set of Jurassic World: Page 4|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/jurassic-world-set-visit/4/|work=Slash Film|date=2015-04-28|accessdate=07-05-2015|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150622090557/http://www.slashfilm.com/jurassic-world-set-visit/4/|archive-date=2015-06-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>

